-LpGajGaZcUJRyLSvl9C.description:
Terrific apartment overlooking the 7th hole on the Cariari Golf Course for sale. Hot looking, modern one bedroom apartment recently totally renovated overlooking the 7th hole of the renown Cariari Golf and Country Club.

The price includes nearly all the furnishing and appliances you see in the pictures.

Come and stay for a lifetime or when you can get away, and when you’re not using it, have it rented out by an administration already in place set up to do so.

Not only will they rent it out (nearly 100% occupancy) but they also have maintenance and cleaning services. You have to do nothing but come around when you can and collect the money when you can’t.

It doesn’t get much better than this.

-LpGbelHtSWZF1F7m0tZ.description:
A great furnished townhouse in the heart of Cariari. This wonderful townhouse is located in front of the Cariari Golf Course. There’s a road between the townhouse and this great golf course, giving you a bit of leeway on those errant drives. The home has everything anyone can hope to have in a townhouse: plenty enough space, nice views front and back, a pleasant backyard.

One attractive feature is the affordable price and it is nice to be able to walk to the clubhouse in minutes and less if you own a golf cart. The airport is only 10 minutes away by car and downtown San Jose a bit more outside the rush hour. The shopping can be done at the local grocery or at the multi-level Cariari Mall. Many fine restaurant grace the area.

-LpunHpYJdeXgWLE6hSl.description:

A newly renovated one-story home with a panoramic view of the mountains. With three bedrooms, two and a half washrooms, swimming pool, kitchen, living room, dining room, family/tv room, office, a great terrace and parking for indoors for two cars.

There’s also a full maids quarters with bathroom and an extra bath for the pool area.

The three bedrooms and the office have air conditioning.

Located in Bosques de Doña Rosa, a lovely and safe neighborhood that’s guarded by guards at the entrance gate and patrols the 24/7.

-LpuocqE3Wn0UJponwkC.description:
This is a very attractive one storey home with plenty of backyard and interior space.

The dwelling consists of three comfortable-sized bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. There is also a maid’s quarters with its own pretty bathroom that could well serve as guest quarters.

As well are a two-car garage, spacious laundry area, a second entrance into the backyard for service people (e.g. gardener), high ceilings with nice wood beams, automatic sprinkler system for the back and front yards, and a large patio overlooking the backyard.

You also have access to the backyard via the French doors from the master bedroom.

This property is located close to the entrance of a gated community called Bosques de Doña Rosa which is a very safe and beautiful area of Cariari.
The private Cariari Golf and Country club with its Tom Fazio designed golf course, 12 tennis courts, Olympic swimming pool, exercise, and fitness center is but a short distance away.

-LrB7iF7YNPWLRGQlsnf.description:
This magnificent home is comprised of three parts. The first one is the main house that was constructed some eight years ago. It has nearly 4,200 square feet of space that includes a living room, a dining room, kitchen with a side tea room, office, guest bathroom, a laundry area and parking for three cars on the lower floor. On the second floor you will find the master bedroom and two adjacent rooms each with its own bathroom.

It must be added that it is fully furnished with the finest furniture and art pieces that you could wish for. The second part is a guest house built some four years ago and it has some 1400 square feet with two large bedrooms, each with its own washroom, a living room and an open kitchen. Again, built and decorated with only the finest materials and furnishings. The third part is a recreational gazebo of some 1,100 square feet overlooking the pool with its own swim-to round bar and cascading water.

This is truly like having your own five-star tropical paradise hotel at your pleasure. The best is that you don't have to go far away to enjoy it!
